This is a basic example program to display Laird SDK Events.

2014-08-06
Updated version to 1.1.2
Adding support for SDC_E_FW_ERROR event

2014-06-04
Updated version to 1.1.1
Adding handling of SIGTERM
Adding --bitmask (-b) option to specify bitmask directly
Fixed bug where --types wouldn't set all event types

2014-05-27
Updated version to 1.1
Adding support for outputting to syslog
Adding options to specify output options and event types

2014-01-28
Adding DOT11_RC_BSS_TRANSIT_MGMT .11 reason code and version print out.

2014-01-23
Adding SDC_E_INTERNAL event parsing.

2014-01-09
Initial version of the example event_mon.
